<a name="Readme"></a>

## Readme(config) ⇒ <code>object</code>
Define a bud for README.md

**Kind**: global function  
**Returns**: <code>object</code> - - Bud object.  

| Param | Type | Default | Description |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| config | <code>object</code> |  | Configuration. |
| config.sections | <code>string</code> |  | Section file path. |
| config.pkg | <code>object</code> |  | Package data. |
| config.repo | <code>string</code> |  | GitHub Repository name. (eg. 'ape-repo/ap-tmpl') |
| config.badges | <code>object</code> |  | Badge data. |
| [config.badges.travis] | <code>boolean</code> | <code>false</code> | Should show travis badge. |
| [config.badges.codeclimate] | <code>boolean</code> | <code>false</code> | Should show codeclimate badge. |
| [config.badges.codeclimateCoverage] | <code>boolean</code> | <code>false</code> | Should show codeclimate coverage badge. |
| [config.badges.gemnasium] | <code>boolean</code> | <code>false</code> | Should show gemnasium badge. |
| [config.badges.npm] | <code>boolean</code> | <code>false</code> | Should show npm badge. |
| [config.badges.bower] | <code>boolean</code> | <code>false</code> | Should show bower badge. |
| config.links | <code>object</code> |  | Link urls. |
| config.overview | <code>string</code> |  | Overview file path. |
| config.vars | <code>object</code> |  | Custom variables. |
